{"tid":1534552,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"留意返2018年諾貝爾和平獎得獎者關注嘅議題係sex violence","createTime":"2019-09-03T04:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T11:16:13.000Z","uid":102255,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c64fc1ca12be76a41be711a82add8c5d43c10441","tid":1534552,"uid":102255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:48:29.000Z","msg":"#metoo 集會嘅一字一句，任何有關性暴力嘅資料一定要輯錄成英文，再增加國際社會關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018年呢屆諾貝爾和平獎得主有兩個，其中一個Nadia Murad 得獎之後就係做緊好多關注性暴力/罪行嘅倡議工作<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/2018_Nobel_Peace_Prize\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2018_Nobel_Peace_Prize&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFGZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=29ecef1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/2018_Nobel_Peace_Prize</a><br />\n<br />\n絕不能讓我地呢班勇敢企出嚟，或者只能啞忍嘅香港女性不明不白。呢筆帳今年唔還，嚟緊十年廿年甚至一百年都應該追究到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自問不才，未必有能力幫手帶頭做一個archive, 但希望拋磚引玉可以凝聚到一班人去做呢樣嘢。呢個唔係玩玩下整幾幅文宣圖send 出去就算，係講緊一個archive, 有qualitative 嘅料，verbatim, 口述歷史咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做完send 俾Nadia 又好Malala 又好，一定要俾國際社會嘅activists 知呢啲嘢係發生緊同發生咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真我都唔知可以點開始，但我諗有心嘅巴絲留個名，tg 又好，希望做得成呢樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fe54a113a877aa711f4d10cee635dafe680c92","tid":1534552,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:48:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81fe389b9003b4d80ceafde827738ae629900fa9","tid":1534552,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:48:50.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc148a26dce6b1ee4cde524f8f9bfecabdd6d604","tid":1534552,"uid":102255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:53:10.000Z","msg":"自推10下，推唔起就byebye"},{"pid":"77c3c2b80725c09e7340e21e2f86fcdd523643c3","tid":1534552,"uid":12864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:06:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3ccca34938b54b05f4fcc610d289e5465be425c","tid":1534552,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:09:06.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出糧換美金 全民提款日</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.07 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.08 美國人權及民主法案大遊行 14:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.13 各區同慶賀中秋 人鏈 19:00 - 22:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.14 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉頭見</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"f6d2e51ccef6aacd4d1f39ecb4ec9790b33ec2c9","tid":1534552,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:09:41.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"aa22b41f39bb2208d2eec5657f9f4f32931069be","tid":1534552,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:12:08.000Z","msg":"好老實 2019 和平獎90% 係屬於香港water revolution 既參與者， 依個係最大既證據證明依場係無大台既運動， 亦都係最大既證明參與者係和平地爭取民主自由， 唔係打飛機， 但還一個公道畀抗爭者係必要既"},{"pid":"2ca646f950f9f71c5899166c00cb2e5eab4bd2a2","tid":1534552,"uid":102255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:19:06.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"d0730783275b988953c1ea20f55676819f13b01f","tid":1534552,"uid":102255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:46:41.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"82f78a3311ba7eeca2602f633e6af4fcd8dd13b2","tid":1534552,"uid":102255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:15:07.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"fd83a3709038134de334306c69633ed9f19d4174","tid":1534552,"uid":102255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:07:36.0